Vending Machine User Stories


1.  User is presented with list of items and related cost or option to exit.  User is prompted to enter money. Prompt user to make item choice.  

2.  If user does not enter enough money advise insufficent funds.  User is prompted to either add more money or to be returned to menu.

3.  If user does not enter more money. User can make a different item selection or exit with change being returned.

4.  If user does enter more money.  Item is deducted from inventory.  Cost is deducted from the money.  Change is returned to the user.

5.  Machine saves inventory and exits.  
